c: 4
v: 32
t: "Soni ngasinyyilupataga ichindu yaapeleche Allah mwawinji kwa ŵane mwa jenumanja kwapunda ŵane, akwete kupata achalume liunjili lya (malipilo ga) yapanganyisye, nombe nao achakongwe akwete kupata liunjili lya (malipililo ga) yapanganyisye, ni mum'bendeje Allah ukoto Wakwe, chisimu Allah chindu chilichose aŵele Jwaachimanya chenene"